## 9. API Endpoints Map

![API Endpoints — 25+ REST and WebSocket endpoints organized into Scan, AI, Data, Reports, and Real-Time categories](C:\Users\mahen\.gemini\antigravity\brain\1f67c5cb-f2fb-408b-9360-5493c5ef10e6\api_endpoints_map_1772912896110.png)

> **25+ API endpoints** covering scanning (12 endpoints), AI chat, statistics, history, news, report sharing, and real-time WebSocket feeds.

